        <div class='post__title__excerpt wysiwyg p italic mb1 mt025 pr2 o4 theme__text ' >
            Promise and controversy continue to surround string theory as a potential unified theory of everything. In the latest episode, Cumrun Vafa discusses his progress in trying to find good, testable models hidden among the "swampland’" of impossible universes.        </div>
